parameters: \n<\n[1]>Got to be the thing bat talked about...\.\.\. \BST[8]of course it had to be stuck inside this huge thing...
\n<\n[1]>How the hell am I supposed to get it out!?\.\. Damnit!!
\n<\n[1]>!!!\.\. Oi,\. small fries!!\.\. What's on your mind?!
\n<\n[1]>Just...\.\.\. don't get in my way,\. I've got a bat to deal with...
\n<\n[1]>Hey!\.\. Told ya to leave me alone!
\n<\n[1]>Maybe...\.\.\. you got something to do with that crystal?
\n<\n[1]>Eh...\.\.\. whatever.\.\. Maybe bat knows more about you guys...\.\.\. \BST[7]she used to live in the Hole...\.\.\. she has to.
\n<\n[1]>I'll get it out,\. just you wait...
